1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,520
You know that afternoon slump,

2
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:03,680
where you suddenly can't care about anything?

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:06,440
It has a name, 1,600 years ago,

4
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:08,800
Desert monks called it acedia,

5
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:10,280
the noonday Demon,

6
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:13,600
a literal demon they believed attacked them at lunchtime.

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,160
And what happened to that demon next

8
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:17,120
is why you feel guilty for resting today.
